-- Banker Arrested in California Over Olympus Corp. Fraud
-- B y   D a v i d   G l o v i n
-- 2012-12-20T22:02:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-20/banker-arrested-in-california-over-olympus-corp-fraud.html
A banker was arrested in California
for allegedly taking part in a scheme to misrepresent the
financial condition of Olympus Corp., federal prosecutors in
Manhattan said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
